Description
  A bash script for Ubuntu to install Tailscale and configure (Dual-stack supported).

Usage
  Firewall ports
    - 443/tcp: used for HTTPS and DERP.
    - 3478/udp: used for STUN.
    - 40000/udp: used for Tailscale Peer Relays.
    - 41641/udp: used for the default WireGuard direct connection.

Tailscale is a registered trademark of Tailscale Inc.
